videos.description: NC State QB Ryan Finley uses his legs to run for a 46-yard gain on the Wolfpack's first play from scrimmage.
videos.headline: Wolfpack's first play goes for big gain on QB keeper

videos.description: After Chase Litton's 1-yard pass to Willie Johnson was initially ruled an incompletion, the referees overturned the call, giving Marshall a touchdown.
videos.headline: Overturned call leads to Marshall TD

videos.description: The Thundering Herd's Keion Davis follows his blockers en route to a huge 53-yard pickup.
videos.headline: Marshall's Davis breaks free for 53-yard scamper

videos.description: Stephen Louis takes the pass from Ryan Finley and breaks tackles on his way to a 24-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: NC State's Louis eludes defenders to score

videos.description: Tyre Brady gets open and spins around his defender before taking it 75 yards to the end zone.
videos.headline: Marshall's Brady burns his man for 75-yard TD

videos.description: NC State breaks out the trick play to score a 39-yard touchdown from Ryan Finley to Jaylen Samuels.
videos.headline: Wolfpack score long TD on flea flicker

videos.description: Jaylen Samuels tips the ball to himself multiple times and adjusts mid-air to make an impressive 23-yard catch.
videos.headline: Wolfpack WR tips ball to himself to make acrobatic grab

videos.description: Reggie Gallaspy II takes the option pitch and outruns the Marshall defender to score from a yard out.
videos.headline: Gallaspy beats defender to the edge for NC State TD

videos.description: Jerod Fernandez forces a Marshall fumble, and Justin Jones recovers it for a big NC State defensive stop.
videos.headline: NC State forces fumble, wins scramble for ball

videos.description: Reggie Gallaspy II  takes the handoff and runs through Marshall defenders en route to a 23-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wolfpack's Gallaspy bowls over defenders for his 2nd TD

videos.description: Chase Litton's pass is intercepted by NC State's Airius Moore deep in Wolfpack territory.
videos.headline: NC State picks off Marshall in the red zone

videos.description: Keith Morehouse and Dustin Fox analyze the action after a competitive game between Marshall and NC State
videos.headline: Marshall v NC State post-game breakdown
